[{"id":"VR860289","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<p class=\"stem_paragraph\">What will be the new distance of the first minimum from the central peak?</p>\n","rubricRef":"VR860289_rubric","features":[{"type":"sharedpassage","html":"<p class=\"stem_paragraph\">A beam of monochromatic light passes through a single slit, as shown, producing a diffraction pattern on a screen. The first minimum is a distance <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"y sub 1\" role=\"math\"><math alttext=\"y sub 1\" overflow=\"scroll\"> <msub> <mi>y</mi> <mn>1</mn> </msub> </math></span></span> from the central peak. The distance between the slit and screen is much greater than <span aria-label=\"y sub 1\" role=\"math\">\\(y_1\\)</span>. The frequency of the light is then doubled.</p>\n\n<div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows a light beam passing through a slit and producing a diffraction pattern on a screen. The first minimum in the diffraction pattern is a distance y sub 1 from the central peak. A note states that the figure is not drawn to scale.\" src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/578/VR860289.g01.svg\" /></div>\n"}],"choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"the fraction with numerator y sub 1, and denominator 4\"><math alttext=\"the fraction with numerator y sub 1, and denominator 4\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mfrac><msub><mi>y</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mn>4</mn></mfrac></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"the fraction with numerator y sub 1, and denominator 2\"><math alttext=\"the fraction with numerator y sub 1, and denominator 2\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mfrac><msub><mi>y</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2 y sub 1\"><math alttext=\"2 y sub 1\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn><msub><mi>y</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"4 y sub 1\"><math alttext=\"4 y sub 1\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>4</mn><msub><mi>y</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></math></span></span></p>"],"answer":1}]